title: Cabo San Pedro - 1 bed - Stunning Ocean Views
description:
Our place is a spacious 1 bedroom/1 bath unit with absolutely stunning views of the San Francisco coastline. From our deck, you can see the Golden Gate Bridge towers, beautiful Pacifica State beach with its many surfers, it is just a fabulously lovely view. We're the highest house on Pedro Point, so we've got the best views in the area!

This is the middle floor of our 3 story duplex house. The upper floor is a studio apartment and the lower floor is another 2 rooms that can go with this unit.
